<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3">
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <!-- Default panel contents -->
        <div class="panel-heading"><strong>{{this.product.title}}</strong></div>
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item"><p>posted {{this.product.datetime}} </p></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="person1" style="float:left; display:inline-block; ">
             <span style="float:left;width: 50%;">
                 <img src="{{this.product.imagePath}}"
                  width="250"/>
             </span>
             <span style="float:right;width: 50%;">
                <p style="float:right; display:block;">{{this.product.description}}</p>
                <p></p>
                <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#ReportModal" href="#myModal">Report this ad</a>
                <div id="ReportModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                  <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <!-- Modal content-->
                    <div class="modal-content">
                      <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                        <h4 class="modal-title"><h3><font color="darkred">Is there something wrong with this ad?</font></h3>
                        <p>We're constantly working hard to assure that our ads meet high standards and we are very grateful for any kind of feedback from our users.</p>
                      </h4>
                      </div>
                      <div class="modal-body">
                        <form action="/report-ad/{{this.product._id}}" method="post" id="checkout-form">
                          <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                              <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="name">Reason</label>
                                <select id="report-reason" name="reason" class="ui-select"><option value="select" selected="selected">-- Select a reason --</option><option value="unavailable">Item sold/unavailable</option><option value="fraud">Fraud</option><option value="duplicate">Duplicate</option><option value="spam">Spam</option><option value="category">Wrong category</option><option value="offensive">Offensive</option><option value="other">Other</option></select>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                              <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="email">Your Email</label>
                                <input type="text" id="email" class="form-control" required name="email" pettern="[a-zA-Z0-9\\+\\.\\_\\%\\-\\+]{1,256}\@[a-zA-Z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9\\-]{0,64}(\.[a-zA-Z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9\\-]{0,25})+">
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                              <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="message">Message</label>
                                <textarea id="message" name="message" class="ui-textarea" placeholder="Message" rows="4" cols="69" required></textarea>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color:darkred">Send report</button>
                        </form>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- List group -->
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item" >
            <div class="block"><font color="gray">Time left: </font> {{ this.product.days }} days</div>
            <div class="block"><font color="gray">Current bid: </font> <strong>Rs:{{ this.product.price }}</strong></div>
            <div class="block">[<a href="/bid-history/{{this.product._id}}">{{ this.product.bids }} bids</a>]</div>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <form action="/bid/{{this.product._id}}" method="post" id="bid-item-form">
              <div class="input-group">
                 <input type="number" class="form-control" id="bid" name="bid" required>
                 <span class="input-group-btn" style="width: 80%;">
                      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Place Bid</button>
                 </span>
              </div>
              <p>Enter Rs:{{ this.product.price }} or more</p>
            </form>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div><!-- Trigger the modal with a button -->

      <p>If two people bid the same amount, the first bid has priority. Also, you can only retract your bid under certain circumstances. <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" href="#myModal">Learn more.</a></p>
      <!-- Modal -->
      <div id="myModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
          <!-- Modal content-->
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
              <h4 class="modal-title">Bidding overview</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <p>Everyone wants to win an auction, but only at the right price. Bidding for items is fun, but keep in mind that each bid you make is a binding contract to buy the item if you win.</p>
              <h3>How to bid</h3>
                <div class="grybg gryBx marT15"><b>Here's how to bid on an  item:</b>
                  <ol style="margin-top: 6px;">
                    <li><div style="padding-left:4px;"><p>Carefully review the item.</p></div></li><li><div style="padding-left:4px;"><p>Click the <b class="boldTxt">Place Bid</b> button. You may need to sign in.</p></div></li>
                    <li><div style="padding-left:4px;"><p>Enter your maximum bid, and then click the <b class="boldTxt">Place Bid</b> button.</p></div></li><li><div style="padding-left:4px;"><p>Review your bid in the Bid History using <font color="blue">[#bid/bids]</font> link shown.</p></div></li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
                <div class="grybg gryBx marT15"><b>Bid history</b>
                    <p>To keep certain info private, we limit how bid history information is displayed. When the highest bid, reserve price, members can't view member-specific information, such as user IDs, on the Bid History page. Though the Bid History: Details page has information on bidders, each bidder is assigned an anonymous name. Only the seller can see a bidder's user ID.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3">
      <p></p>
      <p></p>
    </div>
</div>
